| essql 
  query="SELECT min(fuel_level) as fuel_level FROM \"auto-*\" WHERE fuel_level > 0 "
| math "fuel_level"
| progress shape="semicircle" label="Fuel Gauge" 
  font={font family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" size=12 align="center" color="#FFFFFF" weight="normal" underline=false italic=false} valueColor="#1785b0" valueWeight=12 max=100
| render

| math "odometer"
| metric "Odometer (Miles)" 
  metricFont={font family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" size=60 align="center" color="#FFFFFF" weight="normal" underline=false italic=false} metricFormat="0.0a" 
  labelFont={font family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" size=18 align="center" color="#FFFFFF" weight="normal" underline=false italic=false}
| render

| essql 
  query="SELECT HISTOGRAM(CAST(\"@timestamp\" AS DATE), INTERVAL 1 HOUR) as h, count (*) as wot_events

| pointseries x="h" y="wot_events" color="wot_events"
| plot xaxis={axisConfig position="bottom"} 
  font={font family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" size=14 align="left" color="#FFFFFF" weight="normal" underline=false italic=false} legend=false

| render
